# 🌊 Flowing Water Portfolio

Personal portfolio website built using **HTML + CSS**, inspired by the calm and movement of water.

### 🔗 Live Site
👉 [https://yourusername.github.io](https://yourusername.github.io)

### 🧩 Features
- Flowing gradient header and animated wave line  
- Minimal responsive layout  
- Smooth color palette inspired by the ocean  
- Easy to customize projects, links, and colors  

### 🛠️ How to Update
1. Edit `index.html` directly on GitHub or push updates via Git.  
2. Commit your changes — GitHub Pages redeploys automatically.  

